Author: RosieNP
Text: I have near constant hiccups. Started when I developed bulimia.

Author: phmwls
Text: When I was purging this used to be a biiiiiiig problem. I never thought it could be related to that... but thinking back, it went away since I stopped but it took A WHILE. You are definitely not the only one, my burps were frequent, long, and loud. If I didn’t get them out I’d feel gross. :(
